features.featureTitle: Populate the PRODUCTS array in ProductCatalog.tsx with at least 40 unique tech/gadget products spanning a wide variety of categories (e.g., smartphones, laptops, wearables, audio, smart home, gaming, photography, networking, accessories, drones, VR/AR, health tech, robotics, e-readers). Each product must have a unique id, name, description, price, category, image placeholder or emoji, and a rating.
